# Build artifacts
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.astro
**/.turbo
**/.cache
# Incremental TSC bookkeeping — if these get copied into the image,
# tsc thinks the previous build is still fresh and emits nothing, which
# leaves `dist/` empty and breaks Vite's resolver of @openxiv/shared.
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Local dev
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.production
**/coverage
**/playwright-report
**/test-results

# VCS
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Docs / legacy
_legacy
docs
*.md

# Editor / OS
.idea
.vscode
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
*.log
